    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### 🔍 【系統診斷工具 V2 - 腳本版】\n\n**核心用途：** 由於 `Execute Command` 被停用，我們改用 JavaScript 來檢查路徑。\n\n**執行步驟：**\n1. 點擊「Execute Workflow」。\n2. 點開「Path Tester」節點看 Output。\n\n這會測試多個可能的路徑，直接告訴我們哪一個是可以寫入產品緩存的。",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 500
      },
      "id": "bce6e68b-7270-4ff5-a1aa-bd18d94dbcad",
      "name": "Diagnostic Description",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1008,
        384
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1568,
        784
      ],
      "id": "6c690e89-b4c7-451b-b29c-dbd5ca6a3ae2",
      "name": "Manual Trigger"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const fs = require('fs');\nconst path = require('path');\n\nconst pathsToTest = [\n  './products.json',\n  './data/products.json',\n  './files/products.json',\n  './.n8n/products.json',\n  '/home/node/.n8n/products.json'\n];\n\nconst results = [];\n\nfor (const p of pathsToTest) {\n  let writable = false;\n  let error = null;\n  try {\n    const absPath = path.resolve(p);\n    const dir = path.dirname(absPath);\n    // Check if directory exists and is writable\n    fs.accessSync(dir, fs.constants.W_OK);\n    writable = true;\n  } catch (e) {\n    error = e.message;\n  }\n  results.push({ path: p, absPath: path.resolve(p), writable, error });\n}\n\nreturn { \n  whoami: process.env.USER || 'unknown', \n  cwd: process.cwd(),\n  results \n};"
      },
